Name: Percentage of Queued + Awaiting Assignment out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' out of all cases

Name: Number of times Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs across all cases
Metric: Number of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' activities

Name: Percentage of variants that contain at least one occurrence of Queued + Awaiting Assignment

Metric: Percentage of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' out of all 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Number of Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurrences that appear before Completed + In Call in the same case
Metric: Number of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' activities for cases where activity 'Completed + In Call' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases where Queued + Awaiting Assignment appears and eventually lead to Completed + In Call
Metric: Percentage of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Frequency of Queued + Awaiting Assignment appearing more than once in the same variant

Metric: Percentage of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' out of all cases where 'Accepted + Wait - User' does not happen

Metric: Number of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' activities

Metric: Number of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' activities

Name: Percentage of variants starting with Queued + Awaiting Assignment that include Completed + In Call before resolution
Metric: Percentage of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Percentage of Queued + Awaiting Assignment activities that occur after an initial Accepted + In Progress but before any Completed + In Call
Metric: Percentage of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Number of distinct variants where Queued + Awaiting Assignment appears exactly once and is followed within two steps by Completed + In Call
Metric: the sum of the function base == 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'
